.TH "ipc_update_perm" 9 "ipc_update_perm" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ipc_update_perm \- update the permissions of an ipc object
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ipc_update_perm
.BI "(struct ipc64_perm *in "  ","
.BI "struct kern_ipc_perm *out "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "in" 12
the permission given as input.
.IP "out" 12
the permission of the ipc to set.
